ml_tags: O ALOFA'AGA MO LE TINA PELEINA SUNRISE: 03.09.1961 SUNSET: 05.09.2022 Dearly beloved Wife of Iofi Talatau Filimaua Treasured Mother of Selesa & Fololina REST IN GOD'S ETERNAL PEACE, OUR PROVERBS 31 QUEEN ALWAYS REMEMBERED & NEVER FORGOTTEN Truly loved & sadly missed by your Family & Friends Greatest Nana to all her Grandchildren Tile Filimaua FA'ATA'OTO 31: 25-26 & 29 "O le malosi ma le mamalu e fai mona 'ofu ia; 'ua 'ata'ata fo'i o ia i aso o lumana'i.
